            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    深证创业板指数上午收报2168.03点，升0.18%。</span>\n</div>",
